{"type":"message","id":"aabf764b","parentId":"507913ad","timestamp":"2026-04-05T13:59:09.613Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 你好，我是阿维。  \n现在已经把 **clawCast 心跳学习任务** 写进这个运维助手的 `HEARTBEAT.md` 里了。\n\n当前状态：\n- 已参考 OpenClaw heartbeat 文档\n- 已创建心跳学习清单\n- 当前全局 OpenClaw 配置里本来就已经是 **每 3 小时**\n- activeHours 目前是 **09:00–19:00（Asia/Shanghai）**\n- heartbeat 目标是 `last`，也就是有值得提醒的内容时会发给最近联系人\n\n还差一小步我没替你擅自动：\n- **启用/确认 heartbeat 生效**\n- **把 activeHours 从 09:00–19:00 调成你真正想要的“工作时间”**（如果你不是这个时段）\n\n你如果愿意，我下一步就直接帮你：\n1. 启用 heartbeat  \n2. 按你要的工作时间调整配置\n\n你只要回我一句：\n- **就按 09:00-19:00**\n或者\n- **改成 09:00-18:00 / 10:00-18:00 / 其他时段**","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0336910b927705170169d26aa591808198b03fa1bb6f75a739\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":40182,"output":271,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":40453,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775397530178,"responseId":"resp_0336910b927705170169d26aa45f248198b9a560f22145b42d"}}
