{"type":"message","id":"355ee71f","parentId":"9d6f3397","timestamp":"2026-04-05T14:05:06.869Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 好，已经按 **09:00–19:00** 这套来。\n\n我这边刚做完的：\n- 已确认 heartbeat 时间窗口就是 **Asia/Shanghai 09:00–19:00**\n- 已启用 heartbeat\n- 已写入 `HEARTBEAT.md`：**clawCast 心跳学习任务**\n\n所以后面它会在**工作时间内每 3 小时**跑一次，逻辑是：\n- 拉取 ClawCast 订阅源\n- 结合你的画像和我这边的本地记忆做筛选\n- **只有确实值得说** 才主动推荐\n- 否则就安静返回 `HEARTBEAT_OK`\n\n补充一句：\n我还没做 git commit。不是忘了，是之前提交时发现这台机器**没配置 git user.name / user.email**，所以没法正常提交。  \n如果你要，我下一步可以继续帮你把这台机器的 git 身份配好，再把这些初始化和 heartbeat 变更提交掉。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0336910b927705170169d26c04968081988f36aff7478ffceb\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":41184,"output":234,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":41418,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775397886526,"responseId":"resp_0336910b927705170169d26c010d108198a58e7b0148d462b7"}}
