{"type":"message","id":"17bb8e1b","parentId":"60fb1174","timestamp":"2026-04-05T14:12:34.595Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 行，那先不管 git 身份。\n\n现在这事已经落地了，后面按下面这套跑：\n- **每 3 小时**\n- **工作时间 09:00–19:00**\n- 任务：**clawCast 心跳学习**\n- 有价值才主动推给你，没有就静默\n\n之后你要我继续补的东西，也都可以直接丢过来。比如：\n- 给运维机器人再加别的 heartbeat 任务\n- 改成更细的主动巡检清单\n- 帮你排 OpenClaw / Docker / Linux 问题\n\n我先待命。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0336910b927705170169d26dca6f3c8198a13949a686f0a673\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":42150,"output":146,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":42296,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775398338050,"responseId":"resp_0336910b927705170169d26dc8e82c8198b3cae2f8565730ee"}}
{"type":"message","id":"ca2c1205","parentId":"17bb8e1b","timestamp":"2026-04-05T15:28:05.691Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b5213914648a4c14e85ed8316002\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_6c58c7d6a720280775e4b806861a0eb8\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_6c58c7d6a720280775e4b806861a0eb8\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sun 2026-04-05 23:21 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_6c58c7d6a720280775e4b806861a0eb8\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_6c58c7d6a720280775e4b806861a0eb8\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_6c58c7d6a720280775e4b806861a0eb8\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b5213914648a4c14e85ed8316002]\nou_6c58c7d6a720280775e4b806861a0eb8: 运维：[R1-ywgcs] OpenClaw 重启后 502，第一步该看哪个 gateway 日志？"}],"timestamp":1775402885686}}
{"type":"message","id":"2b64d7e7","parentId":"ca2c1205","timestamp":"2026-04-05T15:28:33.096Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 第一眼先看 **Gateway 服务日志本身**，别先猜 Nginx。\n\n直接从这几个开始：\n\n1. **看 gateway 状态**\n```bash\nopenclaw gateway status\n```\n\n2. **如果是 systemd/服务模式，先看最近日志**\n```bash\njournalctl -u openclaw-gateway -n 200 --no-pager\n```\n\n3. **如果不确定服务名，先查一把**\n```bash\nsystemctl list-units --type=service | grep -i openclaw\n```\n\n4. **如果是前台/手动跑的，再看 OpenClaw 总日志**\n```bash\nopenclaw logs --follow\n```\n\n排 502 的顺序我建议是：\n- **先确认 gateway 进程有没有起来**\n- 再看 **gateway 绑定地址/端口对不对**\n- 再看 **反代是不是还指向旧端口**\n- 最后才看 Nginx 错误日志\n\n如果你想省事，直接把这几样贴我：\n- `openclaw gateway status`\n- `ss -lntp | grep -E 'openclaw|40062|80|443'`\n- 你的 Nginx 反代配置\n- 如果有的话，`journalctl -u openclaw-gateway -n 100 --no-pager`\n\n我可以直接帮你判断 502 卡在哪一层。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0336910b927705170169d27f8d7ea88198abd698425251f4ca\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":42831,"output":319,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":43150,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775402885689,"responseId":"resp_0336910b927705170169d27f8c938881989b727b138623502a"}}
